description: Fantastic West Side two-bedroom with deeded parking! This inviting and well laid-out condominium offers an expansive living room and dining space that is perfect for entertaining all of your friends. The large bedrooms are located on opposite sides of the unit, with both easily accommodating a Queen-sized bed. You will even find room for a home office. The kitchen features Jenn-Air stainless appliances, granite countertops, gas cooking, pendant lighting and warm cherry cabinets. Other highlights include hardwood floors, a Nest thermostat, central AC and in-unit laundry. Located just 2 blocks to the Red Line, your new home is also moments to the restaurants, bars and the beaches for which Southie is known. For those commuting, you will enjoy quick and easy access to I-93 and 90, as well as South Station/Amtrak, the Seaport District and Logan. And the best part about it: your very own off-street parking spot so you can say good-bye to endlessly circling the block.
